# Group Accommodation

## Accommodations Collection [/establishments/{id}/accommodations]

### Retrieve all the Establishment's accommodations [GET]
| Permissions          |
|----------------------|
| `view_establishment` |
| `view_accommodation` |

+ Parameters
    + id (string) ... ID of the establishment

+ Request
    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer my-authorization-token

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (array[Accommodation])

