## Data Structures

### Accommodation
+ id: 1 (number, required)
+ name: Demo accommodation (string, required)
+ description: Lorem ipsum (string, optional)
+ updatedAt: `2019-11-10T12:54:45.000Z` (string, required)

### Accommodation detailed (Accommodation)
+ characteristics (array[Characteristic])
+ services (array[enum[string]])
    + Members
        + `wifi`
        + `dryer`
        + `coffee_machine`
        + `swimming_pool`
        + `elevator`
        + `television`
        + `bath`

### Characteristic
+ type (enum[string])
    + Members
        + `people`
        + `chambers`
        + `single_beds`
        + `double_beds`
        + `bathrooms`
        + `square_meters`
+ value: 4 (string)

### Accommodation Category
+ id: 1 (number, required)
+ name: Demo accommodation category (string, required)
+ description: Lorem ipsum (string, optional)

### Accommodation Category detailed (Accommodation Category)
+ accommodations (array[Accommodation])